## üìÑ Sphinx Configuration (Python)

### Required Theme Setup

```python
# conf.py

# Preferred themes (in order)
html_theme = "furo"  # or "sphinx-book-theme" or "sphinx_rtd_theme"

# Include jbcom branding CSS
html_static_path = ['_static']
html_css_files = ['jbcom-sphinx.css']

# Force dark mode for brand consistency
html_theme_options = {
    "light_css_variables": {},  # Empty for dark-only
    "dark_css_variables": {
        "color-brand-primary": "#06b6d4",
        "color-brand-content": "#06b6d4",
    },
}
```

### CSS File

Copy `jbcom-sphinx.css` to `docs/_static/` directory.

